# Summary
This documentation page explains how to set up webhooks for custom monitors in Amplitude, allowing triggered alerts to be sent to external applications like Slack. It details the webhook configuration process and provides specific instructions for integrating with Slack channels, noting this feature is available only for Enterprise plan customers and those with the Insights package.

